Welcome to Ballywole! Located just 30 minutes south of Dublin City, Ballywole is the gateway to Wicklow, The Garden of Ireland. Widely regarded as one of Ireland’s most charming villages, Ballywole is a wonderful place to visit, live and work in. This site is your virtual guide to Ballywole Village and its surroundings. We hope you enjoy browsing and we would be delighted to receive your feedback.
